=======================
Upgrade from 1.2 to 1.4
=======================

This document provides about upgrade from opOpenSocialPlugin 1.2
to opOpenSocialPlugin 1.4.

If you upgrade this version, you need install OpenPNE 3.6.0 or later.

Way to upgrade
==============

If you want to use inner OpenSocial container like opOpenSocialPlugin 1.2,
you must add a following configuration to OpenPNE.yml:

  opensocial_is_allow_inner_container: true

And if you want to use auto convert encoding about mobile apps like opOpenSocialPlugin 1.2
you must add a following configuration to OpenPNE.yml:

  opensocial_is_auto_convert_encoding: true
